text: Matthew Foster (born 15 January 2000) is an Irish cricketer. He made his first-class debut on 31 March 2019, for Cardiff MCCU against Sussex, as part of the Marylebone Cricket Club University fixtures. He made his List A debut for Northern Knights in the 2019 Inter-Provincial Cup in Ireland on 20 August 2019. He made his Twenty20 debut for Munster Reds in the 2020 Inter-Provincial Trophy on 20 August 2020. ==References== ==External links== * Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Irish cricketers Category:Cardiff MCCU cricketers Category:Munster Reds cricketers Category:Northern Knights cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
